Package: fragilitycurves
Title: R package for developing fragility curves, particularly using ordinal models
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Michele", "Nguyen", , "michele.nguyen@ntu.edu.sg", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-9017-1978"))
Description: Functions and sample datasets for developing fragility curves. Particular focus is given to that built using ordinal regression and its extension to account for spatial correlation in damage.
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.1.1
Imports: 
    TMB (>= 1.7.22), RcppEigen, raster, ggplot2, geoR, gridExtra, stats
LinkingTo: 
    TMB, RcppEigen
Suggests:
    rgdal, sp
